flowchart TD
    A[Start validation] --> B[Load TEA object<br/>collection, artifact, or discovery object]

    B --> C[Compute object digest]
    C --> D[Load detached or inline signature]
    D --> E[Verify signature cryptographically]

    E -->|fail| X1[FAIL<br/>invalid signature]
    E -->|ok| F[Load signing certificate]

    F --> G[Validate certificate profile]
    G -->|fail| X2[FAIL<br/>invalid certificate profile]
    G -->|ok| H[Compute public key fingerprint]

    H --> I{Trust model?}

    I -->|TEA-native| J[Verify SAN contains<br/>manufacturer fingerprint DNS name]
    J -->|fail| X3[FAIL<br/>SAN mismatch]
    J -->|ok| K[Resolve DNS CERT record]
    K --> L{DNSSEC present?}
    L -->|yes| M[Validate DNSSEC]
    M -->|fail| X4[FAIL<br/>DNSSEC validation failed]
    M -->|ok| N[Match DNS certificate to signing certificate]
    L -->|no| N
    N -->|fail| X5[FAIL<br/>DNS certificate mismatch]
    N -->|ok| O[Load timestamp evidence]

    I -->|WebPKI| P[Validate PKIX chain]
    P -->|fail| X6[FAIL<br/>PKIX validation failed]
    P -->|ok| Q[Optional: validate CAA and DNSSEC policy]
    Q --> R{Timestamp present?}
    R -->|yes| O
    R -->|no| S[Proceed without timestamp]

    O --> T[Verify TSA signature]
    T -->|fail| X7[FAIL<br/>invalid TSA signature]
    T -->|ok| U[Verify timestamp binds to signature]
    U -->|fail| X8[FAIL<br/>timestamp binding failed]
    U -->|ok| V[Verify timestamp within certificate validity]
    V -->|fail| X9[FAIL<br/>certificate-time binding failed]
    V -->|ok| W{Transparency required?}

    S --> W

    W -->|yes| Y[Load transparency evidence]
    W -->|no| Z[ACCEPT<br/>validation succeeded]

    Y --> AA[Verify transparency proof or receipt]
    AA -->|fail| X10[FAIL<br/>invalid transparency evidence]
    AA -->|ok| AB[Verify transparency entry binds to signature<br/>or timestamped signature]
    AB -->|fail| X11[FAIL<br/>transparency binding failed]
    AB -->|ok| AC{Multiple logs or witnesses required by policy?}

    AC -->|yes| AD[Verify quorum or multi-log policy]
    AD -->|fail| X12[FAIL<br/>transparency policy not satisfied]
    AD -->|ok| Z
    AC -->|no| Z
    